author: ate
msg: WICKET-926: New Wicket Portlet support: Support for detached/popup pages
- Implementing a somewhat "hacky" solution which involves setting a temporary flag in RequestCycle to indicate the next urlFor call is targetted at a popup page
- Hooking this solution in the Link and ModalWindow as example
There are maybe more locations in the codebase requesting page urls for popup usage, but this should already cover most cases.
